    public interface MetacardType
extends Serializable
    This class describes the set of attributes a Metacard can contain.

        String getName()
        Gets the name of this MetacardType. A MetacardType name must be unique. Two separate MetacardType objects that do not have the same set of AttributeDescriptors should not have the same name.
